metadata.name: Gold is Me
metadata.description:
Nudity is one haze and often times an ambiguous. This project is one of my self defying discovery yet, being free and yourself in your skin is termed a lot as evil, the model in this art has always felt the need to be herself in her own skin and when we spoke in great length and thought of a way to bring that to life we came up with the ‘I am Gold idea’ , to show much value she has in herself and her skin, and the gold with little justice is trying to depict that even though there is no way to put a value on something priceless.
This collection is for everyone who feels that need of being themselves and seeing perfection where society by default sees otherwise, this collection is for you…
